      <title>德国议员同意于 2 月 23 日举行联邦选举</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/german-lawmakers-agree-to-hold-federal-election-on-feb-23</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉谈判情况的政府官员透露，德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨领导的社会民主党与反对派议员达成协议，将于 2 月 23 日提前举行联邦选举。由于讨论机密计划，这些官员不愿透露姓名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/german-lawmakers-agree-to-hold-federal-election-on-feb-23</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 09:38:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国议员接近达成二月提前选举协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/german-lawmakers-close-on-deal-for-early-election-in-february</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据熟悉谈判情况的政府官员透露，德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨领导的社会民主党和反对派议员已接近就在 2 月份提前举行选举达成协议。由于讨论机密计划，这些官员要求匿名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/german-lawmakers-close-on-deal-for-early-election-in-february</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 09:00:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>博雷利称欧盟必须考虑增加对乌克兰的援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/eu-will-have-to-consider-boosting-aid-for-ukraine-borrell-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟最高外交政策官员何塞普·博雷利表示，在唐纳德·特朗普赢得美国总统大选后，欧盟必须“考虑增加对乌克兰的支持”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/eu-will-have-to-consider-boosting-aid-for-ukraine-borrell-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 08:48:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国宣布延长假期以刺激依赖旅游业的经济</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/thailand-declares-extra-holidays-to-spur-tourism-reliant-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国内阁批准明年增加两个假期，以鼓励人们利用长周末出行，刺激旅游业并支持东南亚第二大经济体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-12/thailand-declares-extra-holidays-to-spur-tourism-reliant-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Nov 2024 08:26:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫桑比克反对党领袖呼吁更多抗议，港口面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/mozambican-opposition-leader-urges-protesters-to-disrupt-trade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[莫桑比克反对党领导人维南西奥·蒙德拉纳呼吁对上个月选举结果进行新一轮抗议，并鼓励支持者瞄准与邻国南非和津巴布韦的贸易路线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/mozambican-opposition-leader-urges-protesters-to-disrupt-trade</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 20:40:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普执政下通胀成为焦点，美国国债收益率再度攀升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/bond-investors-set-up-for-jump-in-yields-with-focus-on-trump</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者希望重新点燃上周唐纳德·特朗普赢得总统大选后引发的抛售浪潮，美国国债价格暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/bond-investors-set-up-for-jump-in-yields-with-focus-on-trump</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 20:35:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国将在两年内试行基于区块链的英国政府债券销售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/uk-plans-trial-to-issue-blockchain-based-gilts-within-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府计划在未来两年内开始发行数字政府债券，因为政府一直迟迟未能掌握这项技术。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/uk-plans-trial-to-issue-blockchain-based-gilts-within-two-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 17:43:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普向国会盟友寻求内阁高级职位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/trump-taps-miller-as-deputy-chief-as-immigration-takes-forefront</link>
      <description><![CDATA[候任总统唐纳德·特朗普在扩充内阁时对众议院进行突击搜查，威胁在新政府成立初期削弱众议院议长迈克·约翰逊可能获得的微弱多数。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/trump-taps-miller-as-deputy-chief-as-immigration-takes-forefront</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 16:43:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国官员访台 讨论供应链问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/german-deputy-minister-visits-taiwan-for-talks-on-supply-chains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据柏林政府称，德国经济部副部长本周将访问台湾，与台湾官员和企业高管举行会谈，并将参观台湾半导体制造公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/german-deputy-minister-visits-taiwan-for-talks-on-supply-chains</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 14:40:59 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>毛里求斯三届领导人十年反对后重返政坛</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/mauritian-prime-minister-jugnauth-concedes-election-defeat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纳文钱德拉·拉姆古兰 (Navinchandra Ramgoolam) 曾担任毛里求斯总理三届，十年前被投票罢免，在他领导的四党联盟以压倒性优势赢得周日的选举后，他将重新担任最高职位。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-11/mauritian-prime-minister-jugnauth-concedes-election-defeat</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 11 Nov 2024 10:15:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
